by xabbuh at 2015-12-18T07:09:21Z

@WouterJ When using Symfony 2.8, you [get the 5.6 polyfill package automatically](https://github.com/symfony/symfony/blob/2.8/src/Symfony/Component/Security/Core/composer.json#L21) (Symfony already [uses it internally](https://github.com/symfony/symfony/blob/2.8/src/Symfony/Component/Security/Core/Util/StringUtils.php#L56)).
